query:
SELECT p.id, p.apiId, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice, p.quantityAvailable, p.active,
       s.smshubCode, s.name as service_name, 
       c.name as country_name,
       a.name as api_name
FROM prices p 
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id 
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id 
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.smshubCode = 'test_api'
